Welcome to <%= @user.church.name %>!

Hi <%= @user.name %>,

Your account has been created by a church administrator. To get started, you'll need to set your password.

Click here to set your password:
<%= edit_password_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>

This link will expire in 15 minutes for security reasons. If it expires, you can request a new password reset link from the login page.

Once you've set your password, you'll be able to:
- View and sign up for volunteer opportunities
- Manage your profile and preferences
- Receive notifications about church needs

If you have any questions, please contact your church administrator.

Welcome aboard!
The <%= @user.church.name %> Team
